{"word":"συνεξαιρέω","slug":"συνεξαιρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συνεξαιρέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) (aor2 <el>-εξεῖλον</el>) (ionic <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <el>-εξελέειν</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to take out together, to help in removing</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>:— <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>: <i>to take away also</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to help in taking</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}